## Retry & Timeout Configuration

| Step | Max Retries | Base Delay | Timeout | Notes |
|------|-------------|------------|---------|-------|
| Validate Order | 1 | N/A | 2s | Mostly local, fail fast |
| Reserve Inventory | 3 | 1s | 5s | Network call to inventory |
| Authorize Payment | 2 | 1s | 10s | External payment gateway |
| Create Shipment | 3 | 2s | 8s | Carrier API, may be slow |
| Capture Payment | 3 | 2s | 15s | Critical, must succeed eventually |
| Update Order Status | 3 | 1s | 3s | DB update |
| Send Confirmation | 2 | 1s | 5s | Async, can be eventual |

