## Quick Reference Card

| Concept | Implementation |
|---------|----------------|
| **Saga Type** | Orchestration-based (central coordinator) |
| **Step Definition** | `{ name, execute, compensate }` |
| **Rollback Order** | LIFO (reverse of completed steps) |
| **Retry Algorithm** | Exponential backoff: `delay = base * 2^(attempt-1)` |
| **Idempotency** | Request ID / business key per operation |
| **DLQ Trigger** | After max retries on compensation failure |
| **State Storage** | PostgreSQL/NoSQL after each step |
| **Monitoring** | Track saga duration, failure rates, DLQ size |

